In 2003, Black joined the German heavy metal band Primal Fear, replacing original drummer Klaus Sperling.
In June 2011, Black announced that he would be officially endorsing Pearl Drums.

In late 2015, Black officially joined American heavy metal band W.A.S.P. as their touring drummer after the departure of their previous drummer Mike Dupke.
In 2017, Black left W.A.S.P.  Later in 2018, he joined German thrash metalers Destruction.
